Title: Vis5D Home Page
Body: The distribution consists of two files: vis5d-4.2.tar.Z - source code and documenation (5.4MB) vis5d-data.tar.Z - sample data sets, map files, topography files (4.7MB) If you've used Vis5D in the past you do not need the vis5d-data.tar.Z file since you should already have the files it contains.
